<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#7c82c4dac4cee67c3b3c22516c8f41c9>.
<#7c82c4dac4cee67c3b3c22516c8f41c9> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/b79cb060-8a1f-11ea-a966-bfa48b38ccc2>;
