<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#067b71923874d7deb9d01d71343f11e3>.
<#067b71923874d7deb9d01d71343f11e3> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/9e3c0b20-cdb2-11eb-9269-d991226864d8>;
