    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata.smhi.se/pthbv/api>, <https://www.smhi.se/data/nederbord-och-fuktighet/nederbord/griddad-nederbord--och-temperaturdata>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-12-06"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
