    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/977> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "4adfd874-0a0c-43c3-9e1b-c61ee5463ffd";
