    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/622> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "ec488eb2-c907-41bd-84c5-203c7ad4542d";
