    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/631> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "00cd8b9f-dd23-44ff-91f5-ec701b09d355";
