    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/656> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "96dabb5e-7afd-4590-8fb0-9373044e41dc";
