    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2001-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/1000> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "c8211ea0-0dd0-45b2-b8e4-409bf79721c6";
