    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/689> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "19bd6e9d-ba31-4db5-b94c-c2ee0fe05a0c";
