<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#e97486f04407d8cdd6679270d82b6007>.
<#e97486f04407d8cdd6679270d82b6007> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://statistikdatabasen.scb.se/dataset/TAB6361>;
